BEGIN_TEXT
For each sequence, find a formula for the general term, \( a_n \).
For example, answer \(n ^2 \) if given the sequence: $BR
\( \lbrace 1, 4, 9, 16, 25, 36, . . . \rbrace \)
$BR
\{ ans_rule(15) \}  $questions[$slice[0]]
$BR
\{ ans_rule(15)  \}  $questions[$slice[1]]  

END_TEXT

